    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3463" key="#Princeps">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3639" key="#Other_palatine_officer"
                            >Totonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">thesaurarii</rs> nostri, tibi <name
                            ref="Audefusus">Audefuso</name>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">sartori</rs> nostro modicam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >terrecellam</rs> infra hanc <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/110"
                            >Beneventanam</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs> que est iuxta <rs key="#Houses">casam</rs>
                        <name ref="Petrus">Petri</name> qui fuit <rs
                            key="#Horses #Specialized_workers">marescalcus</rs>, de una parte <rs
                            key="#Fines">coniuncta est</rs> cum <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs>
                        <name ref="Leopardus">Leopardi</name>, et est <rs key="#Size">in longitudine
                            pedes decem et octo, in latitudine pedes quattuordecim</rs>; ipsam vero
                        terrecellam <name ref="Aldechis">Aldechis</name>
                        <rs key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation">absque preceptum
                            tenet</rs>; in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum
                        roboreum preceptum predictam terrecellam ut prelegitur tu et heredes tui
                        habere et possidere valeatis, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est
                        comitibus, gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptum
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3462" key="#Writer">Theodericus</persName>. Actum
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> quarto
                        anno, mense septembrio, sexta indictio. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
